{"tid":1628161,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最暴力嘅文宣戰略","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:56:55.000Z","uid":69159,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc63c94569bac8a861e32bf375882510b2b9813","tid":1628161,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:06:34.000Z","msg":"準備好1-2份文宣設計<br />\n內容係：本店支持香港政府、香港警察止暴制亂<br />\n畫面：開鎗、暴打民眾<br />\n<br />\n玩法<br />\n1）去店內詢問店員，該店鋪立場以及是否願意貼上該文宣<br />\n2）自行貼上並離開（保護好自己）<br />\n<br />\n影響<br />\n1）有助市民罷買行動<br />\n2）清晰店鋪立場<br />\n3）如該店撕走文宣或拒絕貼上，可大肆宣揚<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"6375231df65d96073b8c446fcd2ef9783347830f","tid":1628161,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"有得諗"},{"pid":"e28fba0a96756b0ffa82c3e09f80ba680776b9d0","tid":1628161,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n成班人濫用私了<br />\n<br />\n同721有咩分別？"},{"pid":"c1c21b599d271dc2c970c100ce2ac6b0b53e725c","tid":1628161,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43513240bfa5bcb8311d8d5743eb73c895b708e5","tid":1628161,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e28fba0a96756b0ffa82c3e09f80ba680776b9d0","tid":1628161,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n成班人濫用私了<br />\n<br />\n同721有咩分別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"解釋下點解冇用？"},{"pid":"2afcc90d226131eba24f80dd8b6e14131f1f4f11","tid":1628161,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78a72f6a300fb8f2548cf0d5b8858a9bb955ec79","tid":1628161,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"人地見到間銀行變做燒豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做幾撚多文宣都冇用"